Description:
  Creates a LoopBack application.

Example:

  yo loopback

  This will create:
    package.json: Development packages installed by npm.

    app.js: The main application file.
    app.json: Machine-editable app configuration.

    datasources.json: Definition of data sources.
    models.json: Definition of basic models provided by LoopBack.

    models/ Directory where to put custom model code.
